      <title>“可怕的”清算过后，对冲基金重新涌入加密货币看涨期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hedge-funds-pile-back-into-crypto-call-options-after-horrific-liquidations</link>
