      <title>Schick 剃须刀所有者正在大幅降价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/schick-razor-owner-is-slashing-prices-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销售增长越来越难实现，舒适剃须刀的母公司 Edgewell Personal Care Co. 正在通过减少部分剃须刀刀片手柄中的塑料来降低成本。首席执行官 Rod Little 接受了“彭博未平仓合约”的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/schick-razor-owner-is-slashing-prices-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
